    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not a spark. that’s just something people say to feel better. there’s literally nothing there. i used to see colors, i used to feel every single thing, and now it’s just... hollow. like the vessel is still here but the person inside just stopped existing. it feels more like a funeral for myself than a rough patch.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
